title: SwifTea with The Thrifty Swiftie: Karma is Real
description:
Taylor is truly causing chaos with her Midnights Mayhem with Me.. and she knows it! What track did she reveal last night and what does it all mean? We talk with a bona fide Swiftie expert, @TheThriftySwiftie.. and she gives us an exclusive! Eeekkk!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? What do you think is happening? There's lots of ways to reach us!
